Is there a gold medal for creating cocktails? 🥇
Enjoy the Olympics with your GOLD MEDAL!

🥇 1 oz. Blue Chair Bay Coconut Rum
🥇 .5 oz. simple syrup
🥇 .5 oz. fresh lemon juice
🥇 champagne
🥇 colored sanding sugar, for rimming
🥇 edible gold stars, for garnish

Rim glass with colored sanding sugar. Combine ingredients in a glass and garnish with edible gold stars.
